is on achievement</li>\n  <li>improving life for people less able to help themselves</li>\n  <li>displaying moral courage and vision in making and delivering tough choices</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Honours are given to people involved in different activities, including:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>arts and media</li>\n  <li>health</li>\n  <li>education</li>\n  <li>science and technology</li>\n  <li>economy (including business etc)</li>\n  <li>community, voluntary and local services</li>\n  <li>sport</li>\n  <li>state (including civil service, politicians etc)</li>\n</ul>\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/honours/nominate-someone","slug":"nominate-someone","order":2,"title":"Nominate someone","body":"\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>The person must still be actively involved in the area they’re nominated for.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can nominate anyone. Which honour someone gets is decided by honours committees and their decisions are passed through the Prime Minister to the Queen, who awards the honour.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/documents/digitalasset/dg_193429.pdf\" title=\"Download the 'Nomination pack' (English) (PDF, 149KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download the ‘Nomination pack’ (English) (PDF, 149KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@government/documents/digitalasset/dg_185555.rtf\" title=\"Download the 'Nomination pack' (English) (RTF, 3,698KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download the ‘Nomination pack’ (English) (RTF, 3,698KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@government/documents/digitalasset/dg_185556.rtf\" title=\"Download the 'Nomination pack' (Welsh) (RTF, 1,821KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download the ‘Nomination pack’ (Welsh) (RTF, 1,821KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"form